{"tid":1686740,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"支持“甴近平”, 由你我做起(2)","createTime":"2019-11-01T10:36:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-14T06:34:43.000Z","uid":128594,"like":86,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":98,"replies":[{"pid":"3225fb0b999ffccb02e1cf82c4a2a17dd7882947","tid":1686740,"uid":128594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T10:36:28.000Z","msg":"支持&ldquo;甴近平&rdquo;，由你我做起<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1685916\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1685916</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n多謝大家對是次提議既支持，一日都唔夠就爆左一個post.宜家開第二個post，係希望作出少少聲明<br />\n<br />\n在此，小弟必須在此鄭重聲明, &rdquo;甴近平&rdquo;活動無意去 &rdquo;去人性化&rdquo; 任何人士. 行動目的只不過係想<strong>1.測試中國強大既網絡審查機器</strong>； <strong>2. 利用中國強大既審查機器去幫抗爭者去 &rdquo;去污名化&rdquo;, 令&rdquo; 曱甴&rdquo; 二字被消失</strong>. 所以我希望各位可以對準政權，只針對&rdquo; 甴近平&rdquo; 一人, 以免被有心人利用. 亦希望唔好係國際戰線用, 以免三毛興風作浪.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n希望大家可以繼續係每個留言都加&rdquo;甴近平&rdquo;落去.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nFor those who may have concern about this campaign or being misled by &ldquo;30 cents&rdquo;, I have no intention to &ldquo;Dehumanize&rdquo; any individual. The intentions of this campaign are 1. To test the almighty censorship in China and 2. Try to anti-dehumanize the term &ldquo;cockroaches&rdquo; introduced by Chinese communist party and its followers with the aid of their own censorship. <br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命<br />\n<br />\n最後都係要講一句<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n甴近平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"635aebea291d61e6e98f3f0ef8d2d43e4dcd0b32","tid":1686740,"uid":128594,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T10:37:02.000Z","msg":"繼續一齊甴近平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"343767c094cfc144b4ee133812fb691322bc3527","tid":1686740,"uid":128594,"lik