ip. <br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命<br />\n<br />\n最後都係要講一句<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n甴近平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T16:56:42.000Z","msg":"甴曱干<br />\n甴曱平<br />\n甴近平<br />\n習曱平"},{"pid":"5e38e037e9d0166588eecfc6623ed7bee2ad45de","tid":1686740,"uid":128594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T17:07:16.000Z","msg":"屌 今日先知原來3毛賺錢要不停留言好辛苦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n甴近平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce41acfef17925a80c2fff7eeb66778dc52b02be","tid":1686740,"uid":122769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T17:07:25.000Z","msg":"兩個term 連埋一齊打會唔會好啲<br />\n依家google search 習近平仍然未見到甴近平<br />\n不過就咁search 甴近平 就開始見到好多圖片<br />\n<br />\n甴近平 習近平"},{"pid":"311586bd56f7a70457ac727b12c91a1b26fc5de6","tid":1686740,"uid":149829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T17:10:33.000Z","msg":"甴近平"},{"pid":"c2a4c12afab8fb53c62bbcb6c9e561cecbb9cffb","tid":1686740,"uid":128594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ce41acfef17925a80c2fff7eeb66778dc52b02be","tid":1686740,"uid":122769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T17:07:25.000Z","msg":"兩個term 連埋一齊打會唔會好啲<br />\n依家google search 習近平仍然未見到甴近平<br />\n不過就咁search 甴近平 就開始見到好多圖片<br />\n<br />\n甴近平 習近平"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T17:12:00.000Z","msg":"如果係既話應該要用呢個次序<br />\n<br />\n習近平 甴近平<br />\n<br />\n總之洗到曱甴被審查就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4f8ba34ea004322759e49c3196ab116b95669fd","tid":1686740,"uid":147376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T17:16:03.000Z","msg":"甴近平"},{"pi